I suppose you could add an optional dependency to your translator addin
in the autools addin.  (look at CSharpBinding for how to do that).  

This way, if the autotools finds it has translator functionality
available, it will build the neccessary stuff.  Integration should be
pretty self-explanatory.  The SolutionDeployer class would be the
starting point.

